Key Facts

Build Your Own Bed By Happy Beds

Everyone dreams of being able to design their own bed and our Build Your Own Bed configurator allows you to do exactly that. With over 2 million combinations, we are sure you will be able to find the perfect design for your bedroom. Size, fabric colour, storage options, base depths and headboard shape and style are all customisable.

Read our Build Your Own Bed guide here

Reasons to Buy

  • Elegant bed frame design
  • Available in 3 headboard styles: Lined, Plain, and Buttoned
  • Available in 3 excellent fabrics: Linen, Suede, and Faux Leather
  • Varied range of colours
  • Drawer storage available for 14 and 10 bases
  • Base supported by stunning chrome glider feet
  • Solid Top base for sturdy mattress support
  • Crafted with durable high-quality materials
  • Complies with British Fire Regulations
Fully Customisable
6 sizes, 23 beautiful colours, 22 stylish headboards, 3 base depths and 9 incredible storage options.
Made in the UK
Handmade in the UK using only the finest high quality materials.
Quick Delivery Available
Made to order and always in stock ready for quick delivery.
Easy to Assemble
Less than 5 minutes from delivery to sleeping, with minimal assembly required.

Base Depths (A)

All bed sizes come in depths of 6", 10" and 14". 14" is the standard base depth and will also give you the widest selection and larger storage options.
